properties.name: rest-client.user-agent
properties.description: The user agent string which is used to identify to the server.

properties.name: rest-client.remote.protocol
properties.description: The protocol on which the server can be reached, defaults to http.

properties.name: rest-client.remote.host
properties.description: The hostname or ipAddress of the server, defaults to localhost.

properties.name: rest-client.remote.port
properties.description: The port of the server, defaults to 8080.

properties.name: rest-client.remote.path
properties.description: The context path where the api can be reached, defaults to /.

properties.name: java-fx.initial-height
properties.description: The initial width of the javafx application, defaults to 540.

properties.name: java-fx.initial-width
properties.description: The initial width of the javafx application, defaults to 960.

properties.name: java-fx.title
properties.description: The title of the java fx application.
